      "message": "[warning] Line 34: Every `collaborativeDocumentChanged`/`collaborativeDocumentDelta` signal marks the document unread before re-emitting it, including updates for a document that is currently open locally. That means typing in or viewing an open document can leave a stale unread badge until the document is reopened. Track open documents and/or the update origin, and skip `markDocumentUpdated` for the active local document/session.",
      "revId": "e537aba248f05f13aabe3aa8059b90a64dca990e",
