      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Major] Line 70: The adapter marks every `collaborativeDocumentDelta` / `collaborativeDocumentChanged` signal as unread without knowing whether it came from the local user or whether the document is currently open. If the daemon echoes local edits or sends updates for the active editor, users will see unread document indicators for their own/current edits. Track opened documents and/or have the daemon include the author/source so only remote updates for unopened documents call `markDocumentUpdated()`.",
      "revId": "e537aba248f05f13aabe3aa8059b90a64dca990e",
      "serverId": "1e26b4c1-6b8c-47ff-9df7-501b633d3b5a"
