      "message": "[error] Line 117: Link hrefs from local input or remote deltas are applied without scheme validation. QTextDocument anchors may later be opened by the UI, so `javascript:`, `file:`, or other unsafe schemes can become a code/data-exposure path. Validate and normalize links before setting `AnchorHref`; reject or clear anything outside an allowlist such as http/https/mailto.\n```suggestion\nconst QUrl url(v.toString());\nif (url.isValid() \u0026\u0026 (url.scheme() \u003d\u003d QLatin1String(\"http\")\n                      || url.scheme() \u003d\u003d QLatin1String(\"https\")\n                      || url.scheme() \u003d\u003d QLatin1String(\"mailto\"))) {\n    f.setAnchor(true);\n    f.setAnchorHref(url.toString(QUrl::FullyEncoded));\n    f.setForeground(LINK_COLOR);\n    f.setFontUnderline(true);\n}\n```",
