      "message": "[error] Line 286: Remote delta positions are silently clamped with `qBound`. If a peer sends an invalid retain/delete length, this applies a different operation locally instead of rejecting it, which can make collaborators diverge while appearing successful. Validate the delta against the current document length before mutating the QTextDocument, and abort/report the whole delta when an operation would move outside `[0, docLen]`.\n```suggestion\nif (index \u003c 0 || index + n \u003e docLen) {\n    qWarning() \u003c\u003c \"Invalid collaborative delta range\" \u003c\u003c index \u003c\u003c n \u003c\u003c docLen;\n    applyingRemote_ \u003d false;\n    return;\n}\n```",
